---
title: Carb Smart Chipotle Chicken Bowls with DIY Salsa and Cilantro-Lime Cauliflower 'Rice'
description: Taqueria flavours, in a low carb bowl! Cilantro and lime work double-duty in this recipe to brighten cauliflower rice and add zip to a quick chicken marinade.

